/news/read.nhn?mode=LSD&oid=469&aid=0000135782&cid=1039694&iid=29885584 Hankook Research]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''30.9'''\n| 22.7\n| 11.8\n| 5.7\n| 3.3\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 8.2\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-29\"|27\u201329 Mar 2016\n|[http://media.wix.com/ugd/e7e219_45e8797b0fd3426683d24d0e0c16c06b.pdf R&Search]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''35.8'''\n| 22.4\n| 11.5\n| 8.0\n| \u2013\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 13.4\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-25\"|21\u201325 Mar 2016\n|[http://www.realmeter.net/2016/03/%EA%B3%B5%EC%B2%9C%ED%8C%8C%EB%8F%99-%EC%B5%9C%EA%B3%A0%EC%A1%B0%EB%A1%9C-%EC%83%88%EB%88%84%EB%A6%AC%C2%B7%EB%8D%94%EB%AF%BC%EC%A3%BC-%ED%85%83%EB%B0%AD%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EB%8F%99%EB%B0%98/ Realmeter]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''38.3'''\n| 24.9\n| 14.0\n| 8.5\n| 4.0\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 13.4\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-24\"|22\u201324 Mar 2016\n|[http://www.gallup.co.kr/gallupdb/reportContent.asp?seqNo=739 Gallup Korea]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''39'''\n| 21\n| 8\n| 5\n| \u2013\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 18\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-22\"|21\u201322 Mar 2016\n|[http://media.wix.com/ugd/e7e219_bae1ecd66ea54cb0b55a60205c4a437d.pdf R&Search]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''39.0'''\n| 21.5\n| 11.2\n| 6.9\n| \u2013\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 17.5\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-18\"|14\u201318 Mar 2016\n|[http://www.realmeter.net/2016/03/%EA%B3%B5%EC%B2%9C-%ED%95%99%EC%82%B4-%EB%85%BC%EB%9E%80-%E8%88%87-%EC%88%98%EB%8F%84%EA%B6%8C%EC%84%9C-%ED%81%B0-%ED%8F%AD-%ED%95%98%EB%9D%BD/ Realmeter]\n|{{Party shading/Saenuri}}| '''41.5'''\n| 28.3\n| 12.3\n| 6.9\n| 3.8\n|style=\"background:{{Saenuri Party/meta/color}}; color:white;\"| 13.2\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"2016-03-17\"|15\u201317 Mar 2016\n|[http://www.gallup.co.kr/gallupdb/repor